{
    "content": "<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>首先，这个公告栏有两个文件，分别是：</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">ui/common/randomimagelist.ui</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">ui/common/randomimagewindow.ui</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">如果要删除公告栏，只需要把这两个文件里面的内容清空就行了。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">如果想调出来，就需要把里面的内容还原，这里展示一下里面的内容，需要还原的可直接复制。</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff\"><span style=\"font-size:small\"><span style=\"font-family:微软雅黑\">然后如果需要修改公告栏的NPK贴图，NPK的名字是<span style=\"color:#ff0000\"><strong>sprite_interface2_event_banner.NPK</strong></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>randomimagelist.ui：</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">#PVF_File</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[image]<br />\n&nbsp;[img path]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;`Interface2/Event_Banner/tw_event_popup.img`<br />\n&nbsp;[index]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;0<br />\n[/image]</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#ff0000; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\"><strong>randomimagewindow.ui:</strong></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">#PVF_File</span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#0000ff; font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:small\">[window]<br />\n&nbsp;[type]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;`popup`<br />\n&nbsp;[horizontal alignment]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;`center`<br />\n&nbsp;[vertical alignment]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;`middle`<br />\n&nbsp;[horizontal distance]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;0<br />\n&nbsp;[vertical distance]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;0<br />\n&nbsp;[tile type]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;0<br />\n&nbsp;[title string]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;`訊息`<br />\n&nbsp;[size]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;35&nbsp;32<br />\n&nbsp;[controls]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;[ui controls]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`[image]`<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`0`&nbsp;0&nbsp;0&nbsp;1<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;``&nbsp;0<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;[/ui controls]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;[ui controls]<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`[text button]`<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`1`&nbsp;181&nbsp;392&nbsp;2<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`Interface/WindowCommon.img`<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;`確認`&nbsp;4&nbsp;12&nbsp;13&nbsp;14&nbsp;15<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;[/ui controls]<br />\n&nbsp;[/controls]<br />\n[/window]</span></p>",
